	* src/ephy-window.c:

	Add F5 as accel for reload.

2005-11-17  Christian Persch  <chpe@cvs.gnome.org>

	* src/pdm-dialog.c:

	Set the model's sort column only after filling it. Vastly improves
	delay when opening the PDM dialogue when you have many cookies.

