2005-10-25  Philip Langdale  <philipl@mail.utexas.edu>

	* src/ephy-link-action.c
	* src/ephy-link-action.h:
	(proxy_button_press_event_cb),
	(proxy_button_release_event_cb), (proxy_drag_begin_cb),
